                <h1>Understanding Equity: A Guide to Fairness and Justice</h1>
                <p>Equity refers to fairness and justice in the distribution of resources, opportunities, and benefits. It emphasizes the need to recognize and address systemic inequalities, ensuring that everyone has access to the same opportunities and support. Promoting equity leads to a more balanced society where diverse voices are valued and empowered.</p>
